    "We test both aspects through: (1) an analysis of how outcomes vary based on existing project activity levels, which provide different amounts of contextual information; and (2) an examination of effects following a documented model upgrade to GitHub Copilot in June 2022.",
    "Projects with higher activity typically have more extensive documentation, discussion, and code infrastructure, potentially providing richer context for LLMs to leverage.",
